Telegram users complained about the failure of the new version
iPhone users complained about problems in the work of the Telegram messenger after the update released on September 28.
The user's phone number can be found by his username
Complaints relate to gadgets with the current operating system iOS 12.
According to their owners, after the update, the application shows a white screen or closes immediately.
Representatives of the messenger reacted to the failure.
According to them, the problem may be related to the migration of information to a new application written in the Swift language.
Telegram temporarily suspended the automatic update of the application until the problems are resolved.
On April 13, the Tagansky Court of Moscow satisfied the claim of Roskomnadzor to block the Telegram messenger in Russia.
Three days later, telecom operators began to implement the decision.
The reason was the refusal of the administration of the messenger to provide the FSB with the keys for decrypting correspondence necessary to obtain data on terrorists.
In August, Telegram changed its privacy policy and agreed to disclose the IP address and mobile phone number of a suspected terrorist user upon receipt of a court order.
The audience of Telegram after the blocking in the Russian Federation decreased by 1.2 million
I am happy for the guys who came out to realize the numerical advantage in the match with Dinamo Minsk
Bob Hartley: I'm happy for the guys who came out to realize the numerical advantage in the match against Dinamo Minsk
Avangard head coach Bob Hartley summed up the results of the KHL regular season match against Dinamo Minsk (2:1).
A very important victory for us.
After the match in St. Petersburg, we held a meeting and agreed that we should leave this game behind and prepare for Minsk.
We knew that Dynamo had a good victory before our meeting, so we prepared very seriously.
It was important to score in the majority, I'm happy for the guys who went out to realize the numerical advantage.
We've been playing well in the majority lately, but we couldn't have scored.
Finally, the red light behind the gate came on.
We knew that Minsk would come out charged for the game, would try, and that's how it turned out.
The game in the majority became decisive, we scored the winning goal in unequal lineups.
We managed to have a good third period today, despite the fact that we conceded an early goal in this period and it was clear that it would not be easy in the future.
But we played very well defensively, did not give many chances to the opponent, did not allow us to catch on shifts, Dynamo did not have attacks with a numerical advantage, so everything ended well for us, - the press service of the Omsk club quotes Hartley.
The Ministry of Finance predicts a gradual weakening of the ruble
The Ministry of Finance of Russia predicts a gradual weakening of the ruble against the US dollar in the future until 2035.
This is stated in the bill that the department submitted to the State Duma, writes "Gazeta.ru".
The department estimated that in 2021-2025, one dollar will be worth 66.4 rubles, in 2026-2030 - 71.1 rubles, and in the next five years, 73.9 rubles will be asked for one dollar.
