We are also preparing an action plan to improve the efficiency of the sochi Autodrom infrastructure throughout the year.
This will be an additional tourist product that will give even greater attractiveness to Sochi.
Dmitry Kozak did not bypass the main topic of the day for Russian motorsport fans - the return of Daniil Kvyat to Toro Rosso.
We all congratulate Daniil together and wish him success next season," the deputy prime minister told Izvestia.
He's a budding racer.
